gw.api.graph.print

Class DotAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.graph.print.DotAttributes

  • public class DotAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    The attributes defined for a given DOT graph element (e.g., node or edge). Attributes used by various Graphviz tools are defined here.

    bspies
